Upgrade
    up2date comand
		Need to import the gpg public keys of a source for package signing
		rpm --import RPM-GPG-KEY.txt
		rpm --import /usr/share/doc/redhat-release-*/RPM-GPG-KEY
		Also can download keys from package source like freshrpms.net

Package management
	rpm
		Query Packages
			qa	query all
			qip	query uninstalled package file
			qd	query documentation for specified package
			--checksig      Check GnuPG keys
			--checksig --nogpg      Check only that package not altered.
		Install Packages
			ivh		install, verbose, show hash marks
			Fvh <filenames>     Upgrade all packages only if already installed.
		repositories
			http://atrpms.physik.fu-berlin.de
